# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>The Draconis Combine Mustered Soldiery assigns conventional infantry to garrison roles across its military districts, with district regulars often fielding extra platoons to secure worlds that BattleMech forces cannot permanently garrison. The platoon operates a Thumper artillery piece, the lightest field artillery available. Its explosive rounds can suppress positions and deny terrain at ranges measured in kilometers, giving even a small garrison the ability to shape the battlefield well beyond direct line of sight.</p>
</overview>

